contentrichtext.text: '''William Paget''' may refer to: *[[William Paget, 1st Baron Paget]] (1506–1563), English statesman *[[William Paget, 4th Baron Paget de Beaudesert]] (1572–1629), English colonist *[[William Paget, 5th Baron Paget]] (1609–1678), English peer *[[William Paget, 6th Baron Paget]] (1637–1713), English peer and ambassador *[[William Paget (MP)]] (1769–1794), MP for Anglesey, 1790–1794 *[[Lord William Paget]] (1803–1873), British naval commander and politician {{hndis|Paget, William}}
